    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-minded driver with good bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. Starts, runs, and moves out with a responsive powertrain feel, and it has the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate in an affordable project or commuter. Cosmetics show age and use, but the core package is there: practical, straightforward, and well-suited for someone who wants usable transportation they can improve over time. Great candidate for a daily, shop spare, or light restoration project.",
